<view class="page-shell">
  <view class="hero-card rise-enter">
    <view class="hero-eyebrow">
      <text>DISCOVER</text>
      <text>按口味筛选</text>
    </view>
    <view class="hero-title">别再随便凑一顿饭，先从分类灵感开始。</view>
    <view class="hero-subtitle">先挑今天更想吃荤一点、清爽一点，还是来一碗热汤，再从对应分类里挑出真正想做的菜。</view>
    <view class="hero-metrics">
      <view class="hero-metric">
        <text class="hero-metric-value">{{filteredDishes.length}}</text>
        <text class="hero-metric-label">当前结果</text>
      </view>
      <view class="hero-metric">
        <text class="hero-metric-value">{{selectedCount}}</text>
        <text class="hero-metric-label">已选菜单</text>
      </view>
      <view class="hero-metric">
        <text class="hero-metric-value">{{categoryName}}</text>
        <text class="hero-metric-label">正在浏览</text>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="surface-card section-shell fade-enter">
    <view class="section-head">
      <view class="section-title-wrap">
        <text class="section-kicker">FILTERS</text>
        <text class="section-title">分类筛选</text>
        <text class="section-subtitle">切换分类时会直接重算数量和列表，让你一眼看出当前这一组到底还剩哪些菜。</text>
      </view>
      <text class="result-count">{{filteredDishes.length}} 道</text>
    </view>

    <scroll-view class="category-scroll" scroll-x="true" show-scrollbar="{{false}}">
      <view class="category-row">
        <view class="category-chip {{currentCategory === item.id ? 'active' : ''}}" wx:for="{{categories}}" wx:key="id" bindtap="switchCategory" data-category="{{item.id}}">
          <text class="category-icon">{{item.icon}}</text>
          <text class="category-name">{{item.name}}</text>
          <text class="category-count">{{item.count}} 道</text>
        </view>
      </view>
    </scroll-view>

    <view class="scene-chip-row">
      <view class="scene-chip {{currentSceneMode === item.id ? 'active' : ''}}" wx:for="{{sceneModes}}" wx:key="id" bindtap="switchSceneMode" data-mode="{{item.id}}">
        <text>{{item.label}}</text>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="feedback-banner" wx:if="{{error}}">
      <text>{{error}}</text>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="dish-grid section-shell" wx:if="{{filteredDishes.length > 0}}">
    <view class="dish-card surface-card fade-enter" wx:for="{{filteredDishes}}" wx:key="id">
      <view class="dish-visual" bindtap="goToDetail" data-id="{{item.id}}">
        <image class="dish-image" src="{{item.displayImage || item.image}}" mode="aspectFill"></image>
        <view class="dish-gradient"></view>
        <view class="dish-topline">
          <text class="chip chip-light">{{item.category}}</text>
          <text class="chip chip-mint">{{item.difficulty}}</text>
        </view>
        <view class="dish-copy">
          <text class="dish-name">{{item.name}}</text>
          <text class="dish-desc">{{item.cookingTime}} · {{item.servings}} 人 · {{item.calories}} kcal</text>
        </view>
      </view>
      <view class="dish-footer">
        <view class="dish-stat">
          <text class="stat-label">烹饪时长</text>
          <text class="stat-value">{{item.cookingTime}}</text>
        </view>
        <view class="dish-stat">
          <text class="stat-label">推荐人数</text>
          <text class="stat-value">{{item.servings}} 人</text>
        </view>
      </view>
      <view class="dish-actions">
        <view class="primary-btn select-btn {{item.selected ? 'selected' : ''}}" catchtap="toggleSelect" data-dish="{{item}}">
          <text>{{item.selected ? '已加入菜单' : '加入菜单'}}</text>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="surface-card section-shell empty-panel fade-enter" wx:else>
    <text class="empty-title">这个分类暂时还没有内容</text>
    <text class="empty-desc">可以切换到别的分类看看，或者先回到全部菜谱重新搭配。</text>
    <view class="ghost-btn empty-btn" bindtap="switchCategory" data-category="all">查看全部菜谱</view>
  </view>

  <view class="bottom-dock rise-enter" wx:if="{{selectedCount > 0}}">
    <view class="dock-content">
      <view class="icon-badge">选</view>
      <view class="dock-copy">
        <text class="dock-title">已经选中 {{selectedCount}} 道菜</text>
        <text class="dock-desc">回到首页就能整理成今晚菜单，不用担心刚刚的选择丢失。</text>
      </view>
      <button class="primary-btn dock-action" bindtap="goToMenu">查看菜单</button>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>
